        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里面一个和游戏相关的社团都没有哎。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "奇怪，难道这个时代的人们都不玩游戏了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "安卡希雅，这你倒是想错了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个时代也诞生了很多好的游戏作品，但比起你更熟悉的那个年代，有些潮流已经改变。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "潮流？改变？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
